Manage Kafka stream group member assignments.

Usage:
  confluent kafka streams-group member-assignment [command]

Aliases:
  member-assignment, ma

Available Commands:
  describe    Describe a stream group member assignment.
  list        List Kafka stream group member assignment tasks.

Global Flags:
  -h, --help            Show help for this command.
      --unsafe-trace    Equivalent to -vvvv, but also log HTTP requests and responses which might contain plaintext secrets.
  -v, --verbose count   Increase verbosity (-v for warn, -vv for info, -vvv for debug, -vvvv for trace).

Use "confluent kafka streams-group member-assignment [command] --help" for more information about a command.
